| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2043 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4fd50cf2-5c59-5b30-a593-b1b3c77bf636"
